Interactive Chat Interface: Clean, modern UI with message bubbles, typing indicators, and smooth scrolling
Suggested news topics with quick access buttons
Example news card with summarization functionality
Dynamic response generation based on user queries
User Experience Elements:
Auto-resizing text input
animated typing indicators
aews ticker for breaking headlines

attach article and voice input options (UI only)
Responsive Design: Fully responsive layout using Tailwind CSS
